      "x": 75,
      "y": 693,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 145,
      "text": "Shows available parts the customer can buy.\n\nWhat properties does the user see?\n(Hint: description and price at minimum)\n\nWhat should you NOT show?\n(Items with QOH = 0 or discontinued)\n\nUser picks a quantity (1 to max).\nWhat limits the maximum?\n\nWhat happens if they add the same item twice?",
