      "width": 490,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Each row = one item the customer wants to buy.\n\nIs this stored in the database yet? (No!)\nWhere does the cart live until checkout?\n\nWhat happens if quantity is set to zero?\nWhat prevents quantity from exceeding stock?\n\nWhat calculated values does the user see?\n(Line total, subtotal, tax, grand total)\n\nWhen do these update? (Instantly!)",
