    },
    {
      "id": "return_detail_title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1378,
      "width": 1070,
      "height": 22,
      "text": "Part 2: Return Detail Lines (a list)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff",
      "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 600151
    },
    {
      "id": "return_detail_desc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1408,
      "width": 1070,
      "height": 175,
      "text": "One row per item on the original sale.\n\nFor each item, the user needs to see:\n  - How many were purchased\n  - How many were ALREADY returned (across ALL prior returns)\n  - The original price\n  - Whether the item is refundable\n\nThink about:\n  Which tables give you \"previously returned\" quantity?\n  (Hint: you need to SUM across ALL SaleRefundDetail records for this item)\n\n  What disables the return field? (non-refundable items OR fully returned items)\n  What limits the max return quantity? (purchased - previously returned)\n\n  How is the refund calculated? (apply original discount %, then GST, then total)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#dbeafe",
      "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 600152
